      "comment": "DOONGALLA GLORY (8) filled a minor placing last start at Warrnambool behind Flying Blossom (22.79) in a Bottom Up - Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Good form should continue. ACCIDENTAL (2) is still a maiden after 10 runs but rarely far away, the latest finishing out of the placings when fifth at this track. Worth another chance. TRENTON'S ACE (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (24.88) at Bendigo behind Ringsted in a Bottom Up - Maiden. Has the early speed to give a sight. Can feature again. DANCING MAYA (7) is by Koblenz out of Miss Elsa making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Expected to produce a bold debut.",
